claim.claim-text:
1. A method for manufacturing a lens, comprising:
providing a metal sheet and a stamping mold;
forming a light shield of a predetermined shape and size from the metal sheet using the stamping mold;
providing an injection mold, the injection mold defining a mold cavity, the mold cavity defining a first molding surface that corresponds to the light shield in shape and size;
placing the light shield in the mold cavity, wherein the light shield is pasted to the first molding surface; and
forming a lens with the light shield using the injection mold.
